        <content type="html" xml:base="https://yzzfo.github.io/en/unity/store/easy-save-the-complete-save-game-data-serializer-system/">&lt;p&gt;Easy Save lets you save almost anything with ease across platforms, along with features such as encryption, compression, save slots, cloud storage, spreadsheets, backups, and much more.&lt;br&gt;&lt;p &gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.moodkie.com&#x2F;contact&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Contact Us&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;docs.moodkie.com&#x2F;product&#x2F;easy-save-3&#x2F;es3-guides&#x2F;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Guides&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;docs.moodkie.com&#x2F;product&#x2F;easy-save-3&#x2F;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Docs&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;moodkie.com&#x2F;forum&#x2F;viewforum.php?f=12&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Forum&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;discord.gg&#x2F;VuzHgDxr5c&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Discord&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;docs.moodkie.com&#x2F;easy-save-3&#x2F;getting-started&#x2F;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Getting Started&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;moodkie.com&#x2F;easy-save-unity&#x2F;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Home&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;p &gt;&lt;strong&gt;░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;p &gt;★ On the Asset Store since 2011 ★&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;p &gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why use Easy Save?&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;&#x2F;br&gt;&lt;p &gt;&lt;em&gt;It&#x27;s easy&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;Save your game with just a few clicks using &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;docs.moodkie.com&#x2F;easy-save-3&#x2F;es3-guides&#x2F;auto-save-saving-without-code&#x2F;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Auto Save&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;,&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;&lt;p &gt;